    • Customer

      public Customer​(int id, java.lang.String name, java.lang.String address, int post, long phone, java.lang.String createDate, java.lang.String createdBy, java.lang.String lastUpdate, java.lang.String lastUpdatedBy, int divId)
      Constructor for a valid Customer object.
      Parameters:
      id - An integer pulled from the Customer_ID field from the database.
      name - A string pulled from the Customer_Name field from the database.
      address - A string pulled from the Address field from the database.
      post - An integer pulled from the Postal_Code field from the database.
      phone - A Long pulled from the Phone field from the database.
      createDate - A string representing a date/time pulled from the Create_Date field from the database.
      createdBy - A string representing a user pulled from the Created_By field from the database.
      lastUpdate - A string representing a date/time pulled from the Last_Update field from the database.
      lastUpdatedBy - A string representing a user pulled from the Last_Updated_By field from the database.
      divId - An integer pulled from the Division_ID field from the database.
